    "400906": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Wriothesley",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So this is the \"forbidden zone\"? Honestly, for a place so well-hidden, Paimon sure doesn't see anything special..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "And that is..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What a huge door!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "There are three such isolation gates in total. Generally speaking, I'm the only one who's allowed to go inside. Hence the name, \"forbidden zone.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "Am I correct to assume you're going to run on back and tell your little Fatui friends everything?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Well, er, Paimon wasn't thinking of keeping anything from them..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "Hah. Well, I'd advise you wait until you've seen the whole truth of this place for yourself before deciding whether or not to tell them."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
