    "401001": {
        "Desc": "Return to the dormitories to rest",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ugh... So much has happened, Paimon just feels absolutely exhausted now that she's finally relaxed..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon's super sleepy... Are you sleepy, too...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Yeah, I'm also getting there."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Zzz... Zzz..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(Wow, she really immediately fell asleep.)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm... Delicious... Paimon wants seconds... For free!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(Goodnight.)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": ""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Crowd",
                    "T": "Out of my way! Get out of my way!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Crowd",
                    "T": "What happened? Why is everyone running?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Crowd",
                    "T": "No idea, but something must've happened, stop asking..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh...? Who's yelling... Paimon still wants to sleep..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(...!? What's that sound?)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Paimon, wake up! We need to go out and see what's going on!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "401002": {
        "Desc": "Check on the situation outside",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What happened, why is everyone running around... Hey! What are you doing?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hurried Prisoner",
                    "T": "No time to explain, mate! Goodbye!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Eh? Hey, wait!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What's wrong with these people!? They won't even talk to us!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Cuistot",
                    "T": "They're here! Ah, there you are!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Laverune",
                    "T": "Thank goodness."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Cuistot and Laverune? Do you know what happened here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Cuistot",
                    "T": "We came here especially to inform you! Something seems to have gone terribly wrong just now, His Grace is telling everyone to evacuate and get out of here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Cuistot",
                    "T": "Laverune was saying, you two are new here, and don't have many friends, so you might slip through the cracks. Haven't you heard of stories like that? An evacuation is successfully completed, yet you only find out once you do a headcount that one or two people are missing..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Laverune",
                    "T": "Wait, weren't you the one who brought that up? Why is it suddenly my idea?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Cuistot",
                    "T": "Shut up!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Laverune",
                    "T": "Okay, whatever. The point is, you should come with us."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You said His Grace said to... evacuate \"outwards\"?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Laverune",
                    "T": "Yeah, he said to get as far away as possible, upwards and outwards."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(Then that means whatever happened must have happened down below... Oh no, isn't that gate at the very bottom!?)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh no, it can't be that thing!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Cuistot",
                    "T": "What? Hey! Where are you going!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "We have to go find the Duke! You two, just go and get out! Go on without us!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Laverune",
                    "T": "Hey! Heyyy! ...Be careful!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "401003": {
        "Desc": "Go to the office",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Clorinde",
                    "T": "Alright. Seems like the problem inside has been suppressed."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "Let me guess, we're safe for now?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Neuvillette",
                    "T": "Indeed, but only for now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "I win this bet. You owe me a present."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Clorinde",
                    "T": "Very well, it was indeed just as you said."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Neuvillette",
                    "T": "You made a bet?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "We made a bet on the size of your entourage. Clorinde thought you wouldn't come down by yourself."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Clorinde",
                    "T": "I figured you would have at least brought a few people along for appearances' sake. It appears I underestimated just how confidential the mission was."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "Shouldn't you have gotten used to confidential missions by now? That's just how the courts operate."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Neuvillette",
                    "T": "So... what gift must the loser give? Tea?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Clorinde",
                    "T": "He already has tons of tea in his office. I'm thinking about a set of legal codices."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "That wouldn't happen to be a dig at my lack of legal awareness, would it..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Clorinde",
                    "T": "I'm sure His Grace doesn't consider the Fortress to be outside the law."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Neuvillette",
                    "T": "I was under the impression the residents of a place like this would be uninterested in the legal codices..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "Uh, that was obviously a joke."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Wriothesley",
                    "T": "Anyway, you've still got some unfinished business to attend to in the overworld, correct?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Clorinde",
                    "T": "No need to stay here if you have a pressing matter. We all know you can't leave Palais Mermonia for long."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Neuvillette",
                    "T": "...Thank you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Neuvillette",
                    "T": "(I hope everything went smoothly with the Fatui Harbinger.)"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
